# Spec Kit â€“ Specification Phase

Use the Claude CLI to create or update the feature specification so it satisfies the Spec Kit constitution.

```bash
claude /specify "{{ feature }}" "{{ brief }}"
```

- Replace `{{ feature }}` with the feature identifier used under `specs/`.
- Provide `{{ brief }}` when additional context is available; otherwise supply an empty string.
- The command writes `spec.md` in `specs/{{ feature }}/`.
